SYED SHAH GHULAM GHOUSE MOHIUDDIN & ORS V. SYED SHAH AHMED MORIUDDIN KAMISUL QUADRI [1971] INSC 53; AIR 1971 SC 2184; 1971 (3) SCR 734 (17 February 1971)

